# Toolset snapshots — weekly drift canary

Snapshots written by `bin/audit-toolset-drift.py`. Each file is named
`<YYYY-MM-DD>.json` and contains the `tools[*]` payload retrieved from
every agent's live state. The canary diffs each new snapshot against
the most recent prior file and exits non-zero on drift.

Snapshot retention: keep at least 4 weeks. Older snapshots can be
deleted as the diff history accumulates.
